{"tid":707562,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股壇傳奇】聯交所創立董事臨終前逾8,000萬股票倉大公開","createTime":"2018-06-18T17:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T00:07:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0af83c51a7f914d822f342238f0a841ff11af35b","tid":707562,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180614/large/1528982530_538a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F1528982530_538a.jpg&h=7f177223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳普芬當年創辦九龍證券交易所，及後四會合併，成為聯交所創立董事之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯交所創辦人之一，本港股壇殿堂級人物陳普芬生前分享買股心得，包括公司市值大、留意公司董事背景、一定要派息，遺產文件披露，臨終前持有至少19隻股票，大部份為穩健收息股，如中電(002)、煤氣(003)、滙控(005)等，以本周三(13日)收市價計，目前市值逾8,360萬元，每年收息超過380萬元，平均每月逾30萬元。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示陳普芬遺留19隻股票，絕大部份都好好息，其中市值最大是滙控(005)，持股量約216,274股，以本周三收市價76.65元計，市值約1,657.74萬元，以去年派息計，全年收息約86.51萬元。以收息金額看，涉及最大收息金額股票是電能實業(006)，持股量96,674股，按本周三收市價55.95元計，市值逾540.89萬元，去年收息多達157.58萬元。<br />\n持有大量穩健收息股為主之外，尚有部份股票持有碎股，例如蒙古能源(276)尚餘2172股，連一手也不足，市值341元；有線寬頻(1097)持股量7,208股，同樣不足一手，市值1,160元。<br />\n講到陳普芬，除了當年創立九龍證券交易所，最經典事件是夥拍骨科醫生方心讓等人，將聲稱生產「魚骨」天線的香港天線在九龍證券交易所上市。招股價1元，上市首日最多升2.2倍見3.2元，短短6周升至30元，被諷為「香港黐線」。其後有指在大廈頂豎立鐵線也可接收電視信號，股價未到同年股災已經急插水，其後跌至停牌，最終倒閉清盤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180614/large/1528982473_ba99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F1528982473_ba99.jpg&h=1f5628fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳普芬死後留下19隻股票，見證他揀股心得「一定要派息」，按本周三市價計，每年收息逾380萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58319290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58319290&d=rY9%2FuYhCWQaw6ZA0H4lBVjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fd9592be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58319290&h=9a058ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180615/58319290</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61108aae72df4bd958028b2f2c8643dcf76d9dc2","tid":707562,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:55:40.000Z","msg":"276<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fd148259ee4e499707925e06b265c67fb66afb","tid":707562,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:06:17.000Z","msg":"5 號仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea2fa71aa886de8fe77820d4158fe8ee2dbc2db","tid":707562,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T00:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 276"}]}